flowchart LR
  Start(("start<br/>config"))
  C1(("c1"))
  C2(("c2"))
  C3(("c3"))
  C4(("c4"))
  Accept((("accept<br/>config")))
  Dead(("dead<br/>config"))

  Start --> C1
  Start --> C2
  C1 --> C3
  C2 --> C3
  C2 --> Dead
  C3 --> C4
  C4 --> Accept
  Dead --> Dead

  Reach["<b>Configuration graph</b><br/>vertices are complete machine configurations<br/>edges are legal one-step moves<br/>acceptance asks whether accept is reachable"]

  Savitch["<b>Savitch idea</b><br/>test reachability by recursively choosing a midpoint<br/>store only a few configurations per recursion level"]

  Reach -.-> Start
  C3 -. midpoint .-> Savitch
  Savitch -.-> Accept

